{
  "id": "RAW_21627f",
  "title": "开放 SDK 策略 - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/open-sdk-strategy",
  "date": "2025-09-03 13:00:00",
  "author": "Tom Occhino, Daniel Roe",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"stack-module__UbbKhW__stack stack article-module__9eLiuW__content\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack-module__UbbKhW__stack stack w-full flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"stack-module__UbbKhW__stack stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">At Vercel, our relationship with open source is foundational. We do not build open source software to make money. Rather, we’re building an enduring business that enables us to continue developing great open source software. We believe in improving the default quality of software for everyone, everywhere, whether they are Vercel customers or not. A rising tide lifts all boats.</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <h3 class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper relative group w-full pt-6\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6\" href=\"#against-lock-in\" id=\"against-lock-in\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Against lock-in</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We built Next.js at Vercel, and we’ve learned a lot by doing so.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We’ve seen the way that building open source and managed infrastructure in tandem can create an incredible developer experience and have massive impact. But coupling a project too tightly to one platform can raise questions about openness and control, even if it also accelerates quality and adoption.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">That’s true even when lock-in is unintended.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper relative group w-full pt-6\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6\" href=\"#planting-a-flag\" id=\"planting-a-flag\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Planting a flag</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We believe in open source, community, portability, and freedom of choice, so we want to take some time right now to articulate this commitment as a new ‘Open SDK’ strategy. Here’s what we commit to:</p>\n   <ol class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__orderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Open by default</b>: We commit to building our frameworks, SDKs, and tools in the open, wherever possible, and will default to the most permissive open source licenses in all cases</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Loose coupling, high cohesion</b>: We want what we build to work extremely well on Vercel, but not at the cost of lock-in. We commit to building frameworks, SDKs, and tools that are open, portable, and usable on any platform</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Innovation, then generalization:</b> We will build first on Vercel, where we can iterate fastest to ensure the best end-to-end developer and user experience. And as we become confident projects are mature, we’ll invest in ensuring our SDKs and tools are deployable to any platform</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This is a commitment we want you to hold us to. In the long run, we believe this openness means you’ll be more likely to stay with Vercel. Not because you have to, but because you choose to.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper relative group w-full pt-6\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6\" href=\"#where-it-comes-from\" id=\"where-it-comes-from\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Where it comes from</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This strategy emerged from a series of real world observations and product decisions:</p>\n   <ol class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__orderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>The ubiquity of React: </b>One compelling reason many developers choose React is that it is unopinionated about how and where you deploy it</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Next.js as a standalone choice: </b>Developers wanted to use Next.js to its full potential on other managed platforms. That desire has become a north star for our open strategy</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>The AI SDK: </b>When Vercel acquired the <code>ai</code> npm package name, we knew we had a responsibility to make it platform, and framework-agnostic. That was non-negotiable</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><b>Nuxt and NuxtLabs: </b>With NuxtLabs joining Vercel and core members of the Nuxt and Nitro teams now working alongside us, we have to be crystal clear. We want Vercel to be the place open source creators aspire to be as they build for the open web</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <h3 class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper relative group w-full pt-6\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6\" href=\"#applying-the-strategy\" id=\"applying-the-strategy\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Applying the strategy</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This isn’t about any single framework, whether Next.js or the AI SDK. And it won’t necessarily apply to Vercel’s commercial products, but we're actively applying this strategy across a growing family of libraries and frameworks:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://nuxt.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\"><b>Nuxt</b></a>: Bringing the same design principles to the Vue ecosystem</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://svelte.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\"><b>Svelte</b></a><b>: </b>Enabling high-performance apps with flexible deployment options</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://flags-sdk.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\"><b>Flags</b></a><b>: </b>A portable feature flag system that doesn’t require a specific flag provider</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Plus <a href=\"https://nitro.build/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\">Nitro</a>, <a href=\"https://turborepo.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\">Turborepo</a>, <a href=\"https://swr.vercel.app/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight\">SWR</a>, and more</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h3 class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper relative group w-full pt-6\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6\" href=\"#for-the-web\" id=\"for-the-web\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>For the web</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We believe the best way to build the future of the internet is to invest in open tools, empower developers with freedom and confidence, and to continue raising the bar for what’s possible without being locked in to any single platform.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Business follows quality. Quality follows mission.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Our mission is to build a better web, for everyone.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 阐述其“开放 SDK 策略”，致力于构建开放、可移植和平台无关性的框架与工具，旨在增强开发者能力并避免供应商锁定，同时优先在 Vercel 上进行迭代。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 阐述其“开放 SDK 策略”，致力于构建开放、可移植和平台无关性的框架与工具，旨在增强开发者能力并避免供应商锁定，同时优先在 Vercel 上进行迭代。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了 Vercel 的“开放 SDK 策略”，这是一项重要的承诺，旨在为其框架和工具构建一个开放、可移植和平台无关性的生态系统。Vercel 强调，其开源贡献旨在普遍提高软件质量，而不仅仅服务于其客户。该策略直接解决了对供应商锁定效应的担忧（即使是无意的），并从 Next.js 的开发中吸取了教训。主要承诺包括默认采用宽松许可构建开放性，确保松耦合以实现跨平台的可移植性，并采用“先创新，后推广”的方法，即工具首先在 Vercel 上快速迭代，然后在其他平台进行部署。该策略的制定受到了多个因素的影响，包括 React 的广泛应用、开发者希望在其他平台上使用 Next.js 的需求、AI SDK 的平台无关性以及 NuxtLabs 的整合。Vercel 正在积极地将该策略应用于越来越多的库和框架系列中，包括 Nuxt、Svelte、Flags、Nitro、Turborepo 和 SWR，最终目标是赋予开发者自由和信心，以构建更好的 Web，而无需受限于单一平台。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel 致力于“开放 SDK 策略”，强调开源、可移植性和免受平台锁定的自由。",
      "explanation": "该策略确保框架和工具以开放方式构建，可在任何平台上使用，并优先考虑开发者的选择，避免对特定厂商的依赖，从而培养更健康的生态系统。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该策略包括首先在 Vercel 上构建工具以进行快速迭代，然后将其推广以进行多平台部署。",
      "explanation": "这种方法平衡了 Vercel 快速创新并确保卓越端到端体验的能力，以及其对更广泛平台兼容性和开发者自由的承诺。"
    },
    {
      "point": "这项承诺的驱动力来自于 Next.js 的经验教训、React 的广泛应用以及对诸如 AI SDK 之类的平台无关性工具的需求。",
      "explanation": "现实世界的观察和产品决策强调了开放和可移植解决方案在现代 Web 开发领域的重要性，从而指导了 Vercel 的战略方向。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们致力于提升所有人的软件质量，无论他们是否是 Vercel 的客户。",
    "我们致力于构建开放、可移植且可在任何平台上使用的框架、SDK 和工具。",
    "我们将首先在 Vercel 上进行构建，在那里我们可以最快地进行迭代，以确保最佳的端到端开发者和用户体验。并且，随着我们越来越有信心项目已经成熟，我们将投资于确保我们的 SDK 和工具可以部署到任何平台。",
    "从长远来看，我们相信这种开放性意味着您更有可能留在 Vercel。不是因为您必须这样做，而是因为您选择这样做。",
    "我们的使命是为每个人构建更好的 Web。"
